WEBVTT

00:00:27.030 --> 00:00:27.760 line:80%
Who's there?

00:00:32.080 --> 00:00:33.210 line:80%
Counselor Gongsun.

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:34.830 line:80%
It's the middle of the night.

00:00:34.830 --> 00:00:36.890 line:80%
What are you looking for? Let me help.

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:39.220 line:80%
It's a military secret.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.260 line:80%
What military secret?

00:00:44.780 --> 00:00:46.360 line:80%
I just told you it's a military secret.
Why are you still asking?

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:47.020 line:80%
Move along.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:48.090 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:00:48.820 --> 00:00:49.950 line:80%
Let's go over there.

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:23.360 line:80%
♪ The world is vast ♪

00:01:24.910 --> 00:01:31.060 line:80%
♪ The storm is rising ♪

00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:36.890 line:80%
♪ Day and night ♪

00:01:38.029 --> 00:01:41.700 line:80%
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

00:01:45.580 --> 00:01:50.040 line:80%
♪ All people ♪

00:01:51.059 --> 00:01:56.570 line:80%
♪ Are part of the past ♪

00:01:58.720 --> 00:02:03.610 line:80%
♪ What's the date today? ♪

00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:11.770 line:80%
♪ How lamentable ♪

00:02:16.230 --> 00:02:16.950 line:80%
Counselor.

00:02:19.910 --> 00:02:20.670 line:80%
Come in.

00:02:22.040 --> 00:02:23.860 line:80%
Counselor, it's already past 1 a.m.

00:02:23.860 --> 00:02:26.129 line:80%
You're still injured. Please rest early.

00:02:26.129 --> 00:02:28.190 line:80%
I'll review the secrets a bit longer.

00:02:28.830 --> 00:02:29.640 line:80%
You may leave.

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:30.170 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:17.360 line:80%
Good.

00:03:17.879 --> 00:03:18.920 line:80%
Excellent.

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:22.420 line:80%
There's a rule left by our ancestors:

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:24.270 line:80%
when forging a deadly weapon,

00:03:24.270 --> 00:03:26.530 line:80%
it must draw blood when first sharpened.

00:03:27.320 --> 00:03:30.110 line:80%
Only after tempering
can it leave the furnace.

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:32.980 line:80%
This is to subdue the weapon's spirit,

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:35.430 line:80%
so it won't harm its master.

00:03:35.470 --> 00:03:38.330 line:80%
His Lordship never believes in
such superstition.

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:40.820 line:80%
What kind of blood?

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:43.670 line:80%
Human blood is best.

00:04:08.310 --> 00:04:09.030 line:80%
Someone!

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:13.360 line:80%
Stoke the fire!

00:04:27.280 --> 00:04:31.040 line:80%
Your Lordship, please treat
these two blades well.

00:04:45.150 --> 00:04:45.910 line:80%
It's she

00:04:48.110 --> 00:04:50.570 line:80%
who can bring these two blades
to greatness.

00:06:17.360 --> 00:06:22.670 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:06:22.770 --> 00:06:25.280 line:80%
[Episode 28]

00:06:30.980 --> 00:06:31.580 line:80%
Hyah!

00:06:31.600 --> 00:06:32.190 line:80%
Hyah!

00:06:44.520 --> 00:06:47.480 line:80%
Little Young Master, we won't be able to
hide for much longer.

00:06:47.480 --> 00:06:49.240 line:80%
If it comes down to a fight to the death,

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:50.750 line:80%
I will lure them away.

00:06:50.770 --> 00:06:52.110 line:80%
You just run for your life.

00:06:52.110 --> 00:06:53.310 line:80%
Don't worry about me.

00:06:53.450 --> 00:06:54.650 line:80%
Mr. Xun, don't panic.

00:06:56.810 --> 00:06:59.430 line:80%
Check out these ruts
on this official road—

00:06:59.670 --> 00:07:03.330 line:80%
they clearly show that a sizable force
just passed through ahead.

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:06.480 line:80%
You mean we can ask for help?

00:07:06.750 --> 00:07:09.040 line:80%
But what if it was the Sui Army
that just passed?

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:11.700 line:80%
Wouldn't that be
walking right into their trap?

00:07:13.670 --> 00:07:15.720 line:80%
I once read through
the bamboo scrolls in my fat...

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:17.660 line:80%
In that man's room.

00:07:17.690 --> 00:07:19.600 line:80%
They contain the specifications
of the carriages and horses

00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:23.000 line:80%
of the armies from the three prefectures,
Chong, Yan, and Ji.

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:26.000 line:80%
These ruts belong to the Xie Army.

00:07:30.230 --> 00:07:32.360 line:80%
Little Young Master, what's your age?

00:07:33.750 --> 00:07:34.750 line:80%
I mean, how old are you?

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:35.480 line:80%
Six.

00:07:36.959 --> 00:07:38.310 line:80%
Still so young,

00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:40.870 line:80%
yet you have a photographic memory.

00:07:41.180 --> 00:07:43.780 line:80%
It shows that your talent
is a gift from heaven.

00:07:44.959 --> 00:07:47.070 line:80%
So you're the chosen one.

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:48.790 line:80%
Teacher once taught me:

00:07:48.959 --> 00:07:50.950 line:80%
when choosing between two evils,
take the lesser.

00:07:50.950 --> 00:07:52.550 line:80%
Mr. Xun, we can take a gamble.

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:54.580 line:80%
Aren't you afraid?

00:07:55.240 --> 00:07:56.410 line:80%
If we lose the bet,

00:07:57.110 --> 00:07:59.110 line:80%
we'll die without a burial place.

00:07:59.230 --> 00:08:00.400 line:80%
Mr. Xun, remember:

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:02.170 line:80%
we're not running away—

00:08:02.310 --> 00:08:05.370 line:80%
we're going to fetch reinforcements
to save my mother.

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:08.110 line:80%
Yes! Understood.

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:48.090 line:80%
What time is it?

00:08:49.190 --> 00:08:52.220 line:80%
It's already noon, rise and shine!

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:55.920 line:80%
Sister, you slept for a really long time.

00:08:56.920 --> 00:08:58.650 line:80%
This fish is really delicious.

00:08:59.950 --> 00:09:02.950 line:80%
I couldn't sleep last night
and caught it by the river.

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:10.600 line:80%
You've got it all over your face.

00:09:13.710 --> 00:09:14.350 line:80%
Is it good?

00:09:14.810 --> 00:09:17.410 line:80%
It's really good.
Brother-in-Law grilled it.

00:09:18.870 --> 00:09:20.920 line:80%
How do you know
it was Brother-in-Law who grilled it?

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:23.340 line:80%
Before you found me, Sister,

00:09:23.830 --> 00:09:25.240 line:80%
Brother-in-Law would grill fish for me.

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:26.640 line:80%
It tasted just like this.

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:29.720 line:80%
Then eat more.

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:32.950 line:80%
Sister, I miss Bao'er

00:09:32.950 --> 00:09:34.520 line:80%
and Fairy Sister.

00:09:37.280 --> 00:09:38.240 line:80%
I miss them too.

00:09:41.830 --> 00:09:43.640 line:80%
What a wonderful smell.

00:09:45.950 --> 00:09:46.880 line:80%
Master!

00:09:47.310 --> 00:09:48.480 line:80%
You're here.

00:09:50.730 --> 00:09:52.760 line:80%
Elder, you look like a sage
from a painting—

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:55.120 line:80%
like one of the stone statues
in Confucius' temple.

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.590 line:80%
I look like Confucius?

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.640 line:80%
I'm really flattered.

00:09:59.310 --> 00:10:01.070 line:80%
You two sisters—the older one's
a bit simple and straightforward,

00:10:01.070 --> 00:10:03.800 line:80%
while the younger one sure knows
how to sweet-talk.

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:07.350 line:80%
Come here, you little sweet talker.

00:10:07.350 --> 00:10:09.850 line:80%
Let this old man take a good look at you.

00:10:19.430 --> 00:10:22.380 line:80%
This girl is truly blessed with
great fortune.

00:10:24.190 --> 00:10:26.950 line:80%
With an older sister like you
protecting her all these years,

00:10:26.950 --> 00:10:29.920 line:80%
she's bound to have great fortune
later in life.

00:10:29.970 --> 00:10:31.570 line:80%
Mr. Zhao said the same thing.

00:10:31.640 --> 00:10:33.180 line:80%
He said her round face
is a sign of good luck.

00:10:33.180 --> 00:10:34.130 line:80%
Old Zhao?

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:39.350 line:80%
How can his physiognomy skills
possibly compare to mine?

00:10:40.450 --> 00:10:42.310 line:80%
Well, I don't know how to compare.

00:10:42.520 --> 00:10:44.280 line:80%
I just hope you're both right,

00:10:44.310 --> 00:10:45.570 line:80%
and she stays healthy.

00:10:46.120 --> 00:10:46.800 line:80%
Alright.

00:10:47.470 --> 00:10:49.950 line:80%
Come on, let me feel your skull.

00:10:58.430 --> 00:10:59.430 line:80%
This girl's fate

00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:02.640 line:80%
holds too much wealth and honor.

00:11:03.520 --> 00:11:05.120 line:80%
Her body can't quite bear it,

00:11:05.470 --> 00:11:08.000 line:80%
so she's naturally somewhat frail.

00:11:08.160 --> 00:11:09.960 line:80%
But with you there to steady her,

00:11:10.110 --> 00:11:11.570 line:80%
that too is Heaven's will.

00:11:13.060 --> 00:11:14.320 line:80%
You don't understand?

00:11:17.190 --> 00:11:18.550 line:80%
Before she comes of age,

00:11:18.840 --> 00:11:22.870 line:80%
you must keep her by your side.

00:11:22.950 --> 00:11:24.020 line:80%
I certainly will.

00:11:26.040 --> 00:11:26.640 line:80%
Good.

00:11:27.670 --> 00:11:31.800 line:80%
Changyu, I have a few things I'd like to
speak with you about from the heart.

00:11:33.650 --> 00:11:34.650 line:80%
Here, Changning.

00:11:34.830 --> 00:11:36.330 line:80%
Go play with Brother Jiu.

00:11:36.590 --> 00:11:37.550 line:80%
Okay.

00:11:38.280 --> 00:11:39.470 line:80%
Be careful.

00:11:45.520 --> 00:11:46.430 line:80%
Last night,

00:11:46.430 --> 00:11:50.120 line:80%
I heard you killed Shi Hu
with just 3 hammer strikes.

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:51.800 line:80%
I was truly shocked.

00:11:52.070 --> 00:11:56.240 line:80%
He was a fierce general, you know,
the bravest among the Three Armies.

00:11:56.460 --> 00:11:57.710 line:80%
It was 2 strikes, actually.

00:11:57.710 --> 00:11:58.470 line:80%
Two strikes?

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.240 line:80%
I also just found out

00:12:01.640 --> 00:12:04.590 line:80%
that you're some Minister or Grand Tutor.

00:12:04.830 --> 00:12:06.200 line:80%
Anyway, you're very impressive.

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:08.000 line:80%
If Jin Yuanbao and the others knew

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:10.660 line:80%
they once repaired a dam
with a big shot like you,

00:12:10.760 --> 00:12:12.820 line:80%
they'd be bragging about it forever.

00:12:13.310 --> 00:12:15.440 line:80%
Are those little brats all doing well?

00:12:15.550 --> 00:12:16.750 line:80%
They're still alive.

00:12:17.040 --> 00:12:19.570 line:80%
Alive. That's good.
As long as they're alive.

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:21.400 line:80%
Changyu,

00:12:21.760 --> 00:12:22.710 line:80%
back to business.

00:12:22.710 --> 00:12:23.920 line:80%
I'll be frank—

00:12:24.880 --> 00:12:26.350 line:80%
someone asked me

00:12:26.470 --> 00:12:28.280 line:80%
to adopt you as my goddaughter.

00:12:29.040 --> 00:12:29.840 line:80%
Goddaughter?

00:12:31.070 --> 00:12:32.930 line:80%
But I'm already your apprentice.

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:35.310 line:80%
That's different.

00:12:41.590 --> 00:12:43.250 line:80%
Xie Zheng sent you, didn't he?

00:12:53.400 --> 00:12:56.160 line:80%
Grand Tutor, I appreciate your kindness.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:58.800 line:80%
But I don't want to rely on anyone

00:12:58.830 --> 00:13:00.430 line:80%
to raise my status.

00:13:00.830 --> 00:13:02.760 line:80%
I may just be a butcher from Lin'an,

00:13:03.070 --> 00:13:05.400 line:80%
but I can support myself
with my own hands,

00:13:05.400 --> 00:13:07.130 line:80%
and I can support my sister too.

00:13:07.280 --> 00:13:09.000 line:80%
I don't think my status

00:13:09.070 --> 00:13:10.670 line:80%
is anything to be ashamed of.

00:13:12.620 --> 00:13:14.050 line:80%
But if he dislikes it,

00:13:15.190 --> 00:13:16.280 line:80%
then so be it.

00:13:16.760 --> 00:13:18.690 line:80%
Anyway, the one I like is Yan Zheng.

00:13:19.240 --> 00:13:21.760 line:80%
I don't want to aim above my station with
the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:13:21.760 --> 00:13:23.250 line:80%
This isn't a storybook.

00:13:23.670 --> 00:13:25.870 line:80%
Not every sparrow turns into a phoenix.

00:13:26.160 --> 00:13:28.670 line:80%
Good. Well said—

00:13:29.310 --> 00:13:30.470 line:80%
rely on yourself;

00:13:30.520 --> 00:13:32.520 line:80%
the strong grow stronger
through their own efforts.

00:13:32.520 --> 00:13:34.940 line:80%
But I have to speak up

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:36.520 line:80%
for that bratty apprentice of mine.

00:13:36.520 --> 00:13:39.520 line:80%
He has never looked down on your status.

00:13:40.120 --> 00:13:41.450 line:80%
He just wants there to be

00:13:41.950 --> 00:13:44.120 line:80%
one more person to protect you.

00:13:44.950 --> 00:13:46.350 line:80%
Although I'm not much,

00:13:46.350 --> 00:13:48.670 line:80%
I've still got some reputation.

00:13:49.350 --> 00:13:50.880 line:80%
If someone tries to harm you,

00:13:50.880 --> 00:13:52.880 line:80%
I will protect you.

00:13:53.070 --> 00:13:54.680 line:80%
Who would harm me?

00:13:56.120 --> 00:13:58.310 line:80%
Just because there isn't now
doesn't mean there never will be.

00:13:58.310 --> 00:14:00.520 line:80%
What if there is in the future?

00:14:02.160 --> 00:14:04.350 line:80%
If someone really wants to harm me,

00:14:04.850 --> 00:14:06.930 line:80%
can relying on a man protect me?

00:14:07.880 --> 00:14:10.280 line:80%
Or can your reputation protect me, Master?

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:13.450 line:80%
Even if you can protect me for a while,

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:15.830 line:80%
can you protect me for a lifetime?

00:14:15.830 --> 00:14:16.350 line:80%
You...

00:14:17.190 --> 00:14:19.240 line:80%
Y-You little girl.

00:14:19.280 --> 00:14:21.610 line:80%
You see things even more clearly
than I do.

00:14:23.350 --> 00:14:24.950 line:80%
A jade pendant found by chance

00:14:24.950 --> 00:14:26.610 line:80%
must eventually be returned.

00:14:27.560 --> 00:14:31.170 line:80%
When I saw him majestically
become the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:14:32.350 --> 00:14:33.430 line:80%
I understood.

00:14:35.020 --> 00:14:37.080 line:80%
I understood why he hid his identity,

00:14:38.030 --> 00:14:39.960 line:80%
and why he wouldn't stay in Lin'an.

00:14:42.920 --> 00:14:44.320 line:80%
You may not lack a father,

00:14:45.670 --> 00:14:49.230 line:80%
but I lack a daughter.

00:14:49.550 --> 00:14:52.120 line:80%
Otherwise, I'll die alone.

00:14:53.760 --> 00:14:55.920 line:80%
I want to adopt you as my goddaughter.

00:14:56.350 --> 00:14:59.040 line:80%
Our fates have brought us together.

00:14:59.430 --> 00:15:01.710 line:80%
If you accept me as your godfather,

00:15:01.710 --> 00:15:04.180 line:80%
I'll treat you as my own

00:15:04.310 --> 00:15:08.240 line:80%
and protect you for a lifetime,
keeping you safe and happy.

00:15:12.520 --> 00:15:13.670 line:80%
Think it over carefully.

00:15:13.670 --> 00:15:15.520 line:80%
I will not force you.

00:15:20.430 --> 00:15:22.290 line:80%
On the day of the dam lot-drawing,

00:15:22.470 --> 00:15:25.070 line:80%
you were already protecting me
with your life.

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:29.250 line:80%
I've also said I'm willing to
take care of you for the rest of your life.

00:15:29.830 --> 00:15:32.550 line:80%
But if you insist on making it official—

00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:39.120 line:80%
Godfather,

00:15:39.760 --> 00:15:40.960 line:80%
please accept my bow.

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:52.400 line:80%
Please, get up.

00:15:52.710 --> 00:15:53.950 line:80%
Come on, get up.

00:15:54.920 --> 00:15:57.550 line:80%
So... So you've accepted me
as your godfather?

00:15:57.550 --> 00:15:59.280 line:80%
Wonderful. This is wonderful.

00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:03.590 line:80%
I've lived half my life in loneliness.

00:16:03.590 --> 00:16:05.280 line:80%
I never expected I'd be blessed

00:16:05.280 --> 00:16:08.590 line:80%
with such a wonderful daughter in the end.

00:16:13.400 --> 00:16:14.120 line:80%
Daughter.

00:16:17.800 --> 00:16:18.310 line:80%
I...

00:16:18.990 --> 00:16:22.660 line:80%
I should be giving you a gift
to mark this occasion.

00:16:23.350 --> 00:16:26.400 line:80%
B-But I've got no worldly possessions.

00:16:27.880 --> 00:16:30.880 line:80%
How about this? I'll give you
a courtesy name.

00:16:33.450 --> 00:16:35.180 line:80%
You were born in the Year of Yin,

00:16:35.710 --> 00:16:37.310 line:80%
so your zodiac sign is Tiger.

00:16:37.310 --> 00:16:38.710 line:80%
Your name is Changyu,

00:16:39.800 --> 00:16:41.920 line:80%
which implies uprightness and grace

00:16:42.240 --> 00:16:45.400 line:80%
but suppresses your sharp spirit.

00:16:45.410 --> 00:16:51.170 line:80%
[Shanjun]

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:47.900 line:80%
I'll give you a courtesy name.

00:16:51.550 --> 00:16:53.310 line:80%
Shanjun.

00:16:54.550 --> 00:16:56.680 line:80%
Meaning a gentleman of the mountains?

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:00.240 line:80%
You can interpret it that way,

00:17:00.350 --> 00:17:02.760 line:80%
but it also carries another meaning—

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:06.310 line:80%
a fierce tiger of the mountains.

00:17:06.800 --> 00:17:09.389 line:80%
A tigress of the mountains...

00:17:11.680 --> 00:17:12.830 line:80%
I like this!

00:17:12.909 --> 00:17:15.480 line:80%
It sounds much better than
Lord Li's "Threshold".

00:17:15.480 --> 00:17:16.720 line:80%
Look at you.

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:19.960 line:80%
Why do you always focus on
the unpleasant parts?

00:17:23.110 --> 00:17:24.960 line:80%
Shanjun.

00:17:26.210 --> 00:17:28.670 line:80%
[Xie]

00:17:28.720 --> 00:17:31.310 line:80%
[Marquis of Wu'an]

00:18:01.870 --> 00:18:03.800 line:80%
Although we won this battle,

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:06.630 line:80%
the casualties were heavy.

00:18:07.150 --> 00:18:11.000 line:80%
The battle of Lucheng
will likely be even harder.

00:18:12.040 --> 00:18:16.030 line:80%
The Yanzhou Army is about to depart

00:18:16.780 --> 00:18:18.310 line:80%
for Lucheng.

00:18:20.520 --> 00:18:24.210 line:80%
Are you going with
that bratty apprentice of mine?

00:18:29.720 --> 00:18:30.280 line:80%
No.

00:18:33.040 --> 00:18:34.840 line:80%
I know he's the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:18:36.020 --> 00:18:38.480 line:80%
so I needn't worry about
his safety anymore.

00:18:40.850 --> 00:18:41.770 line:80%
I want to leave.

00:18:43.240 --> 00:18:44.310 line:80%
He has his duties,

00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:46.520 line:80%
and I have my work.

00:18:47.890 --> 00:18:50.350 line:80%
I want to help
the displaced people of Lin'an

00:18:50.870 --> 00:18:52.350 line:80%
return home safely.

00:18:53.390 --> 00:18:54.960 line:80%
I want families reunited,

00:18:57.140 --> 00:18:58.530 line:80%
working their jobs,

00:18:59.080 --> 00:19:00.360 line:80%
eating their meals,

00:19:01.520 --> 00:19:03.120 line:80%
and living their lives well.

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:05.680 line:80%
With your merits,

00:19:06.110 --> 00:19:08.110 line:80%
you could be appointed Commandant,

00:19:08.150 --> 00:19:10.240 line:80%
a sixth-rank official.

00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:14.760 line:80%
That would make you
the first female Commandant of Great Yin.

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:16.400 line:80%
Are you willing to give up

00:19:16.550 --> 00:19:18.440 line:80%
such glory?

00:19:21.150 --> 00:19:21.960 line:80%
Godfather.

00:19:24.650 --> 00:19:26.980 line:80%
I don't like the feeling of killing
at all.

00:19:27.350 --> 00:19:28.000 line:80%
Right,

00:19:29.870 --> 00:19:32.730 line:80%
the rebels who disrupt our Great Yin
deserve to die.

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:35.330 line:80%
But when I see them on the battlefield,

00:19:35.420 --> 00:19:36.440 line:80%
wailing in terror

00:19:36.440 --> 00:19:37.700 line:80%
and begging for mercy,

00:19:38.550 --> 00:19:40.590 line:80%
I think of Mr. Zhao who was taken away,

00:19:40.590 --> 00:19:42.390 line:80%
as well as Mr. Jin and the others,

00:19:42.590 --> 00:19:45.520 line:80%
and also Granny Kang's youngest son
who died in battle.

00:19:45.520 --> 00:19:47.780 line:80%
I think of the innocent people of Lin'an.

00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:50.040 line:80%
None of them wanted to fight,

00:19:51.630 --> 00:19:52.890 line:80%
but because of the war,

00:19:54.350 --> 00:19:56.080 line:80%
they were sent to their deaths.

00:19:57.040 --> 00:19:58.280 line:80%
I don't want to see

00:19:59.870 --> 00:20:01.670 line:80%
this kind of suffering anymore.

00:20:05.150 --> 00:20:08.390 line:80%
[Xie]

00:20:08.440 --> 00:20:09.370 line:80%
You're leaving?

00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:13.660 line:80%
You know how foul-tempered
your husband is.

00:20:13.830 --> 00:20:15.110 line:80%
If you tell him,

00:20:15.260 --> 00:20:17.390 line:80%
he'll surely tie you to him if he has to.

00:20:18.110 --> 00:20:18.950 line:80%
I know.

00:20:19.480 --> 00:20:20.540 line:80%
That's exactly why

00:20:21.110 --> 00:20:22.510 line:80%
I'm asking for your help.

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:25.120 line:80%
There's too much between us

00:20:25.590 --> 00:20:27.050 line:80%
that cannot be sorted out.

00:20:27.800 --> 00:20:30.350 line:80%
But right now, I've got something
more important to do.

00:20:30.350 --> 00:20:31.870 line:80%
What's so important?

00:20:32.770 --> 00:20:34.570 line:80%
I need to go find a friend of mine.

00:20:35.230 --> 00:20:36.850 line:80%
I can only rest easy

00:20:37.110 --> 00:20:38.570 line:80%
if she and her son are safe.

00:20:40.910 --> 00:20:42.550 line:80%
If it were any other woman,

00:20:42.960 --> 00:20:44.490 line:80%
I would certainly stop her.

00:20:44.660 --> 00:20:46.010 line:80%
But you're Fan Changyu.

00:20:46.480 --> 00:20:49.310 line:80%
You're the one who killed Shi Hu
with 2 hammer strikes.

00:20:49.310 --> 00:20:50.530 line:80%
In all of Great Yin,

00:20:50.590 --> 00:20:52.070 line:80%
aside from the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:20:52.070 --> 00:20:54.270 line:80%
I doubt there's a third person like you.

00:20:55.590 --> 00:20:57.920 line:80%
Is there anything else
I can help you with?

00:20:58.870 --> 00:21:00.000 line:80%
Actually, there is.

00:21:00.350 --> 00:21:01.760 line:80%
Please help me send Changning

00:21:01.760 --> 00:21:04.690 line:80%
and Mr. Zhao from the Wu River barracks

00:21:04.960 --> 00:21:06.400 line:80%
back together

00:21:06.430 --> 00:21:08.130 line:80%
to Mrs. Zhao in Jizhou.

00:21:12.440 --> 00:21:14.640 line:80%
You're not actually a royal physician,

00:21:14.910 --> 00:21:16.550 line:80%
and your name isn't Qi Beholden,

00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:17.110 line:80%
right?

00:21:18.310 --> 00:21:20.170 line:80%
Yan Zheng is the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:21:20.830 --> 00:21:22.000 line:80%
You know him well,

00:21:23.350 --> 00:21:25.250 line:80%
so you must be of high status too.

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:29.510 line:80%
You'll find out one day.

00:21:30.800 --> 00:21:31.760 line:80%
But for now,

00:21:32.530 --> 00:21:35.190 line:80%
you and I are just comrades
who fought together.

00:21:38.350 --> 00:21:39.810 line:80%
Take care on your journey.

00:21:40.830 --> 00:21:41.590 line:80%
Remember—

00:21:43.280 --> 00:21:44.140 line:80%
stay safe.

00:21:54.070 --> 00:21:55.070 line:80%
You take care too.

00:22:00.590 --> 00:22:01.870 line:80%
On the road to Lucheng,

00:22:02.090 --> 00:22:04.290 line:80%
Lord Changxin has likely set an ambush.

00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:08.860 line:80%
Since we can't face them head-on,

00:22:09.110 --> 00:22:11.570 line:80%
we might as well
circle around from the back.

00:22:12.310 --> 00:22:13.390 line:80%
If we do that,

00:22:13.960 --> 00:22:15.820 line:80%
the journey will be twice as long.

00:22:18.240 --> 00:22:19.040 line:80%
We must set off

00:22:19.050 --> 00:22:19.900 line:80%
before dawn.

00:22:20.500 --> 00:22:22.230 line:80%
Alright. I'll give the order.

00:22:22.250 --> 00:22:23.960 line:80%
We'll leave at the fifth watch.

00:22:23.960 --> 00:22:25.510 line:80%
My Lord! Her Ladyship...

00:22:25.630 --> 00:22:26.550 line:80%
Her Ladyship is missing.

00:22:26.550 --> 00:22:28.410 line:80%
This letter was found in her tent.

00:22:29.930 --> 00:22:31.860 line:80%
[To Marquis of Wu'an]

00:22:35.650 --> 00:22:37.350 line:80%
[Got things to do. Don't look for me.
Changyu]

00:22:41.280 --> 00:22:42.800 line:80%
Xie Jiu, saddle my horse!

00:22:42.960 --> 00:22:43.550 line:80%
Yes.

00:22:52.280 --> 00:22:53.150 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:22:58.440 --> 00:23:00.040 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is here.

00:23:00.480 --> 00:23:01.940 line:80%
We'll hold him off for you.

00:23:02.590 --> 00:23:03.200 line:80%
No need.

00:23:04.350 --> 00:23:06.680 line:80%
I failed to explain things to him clearly.

00:23:07.150 --> 00:23:08.080 line:80%
You go ahead.

00:23:08.200 --> 00:23:09.730 line:80%
We'll wait for you up ahead.

00:23:21.680 --> 00:23:22.480 line:80%
Fan Changyu.

00:23:23.150 --> 00:23:24.870 line:80%
Why would you rather
leave a letter and run away

00:23:24.870 --> 00:23:26.200 line:80%
than stay with me?

00:23:29.830 --> 00:23:31.310 line:80%
Why won't you like me?

00:23:32.550 --> 00:23:34.750 line:80%
What exactly did I, Xie Zheng, do wrong?

00:23:42.780 --> 00:23:44.590 line:80%
How could I not like you?

00:23:45.680 --> 00:23:46.960 line:80%
If I didn't like you,

00:23:48.870 --> 00:23:50.470 line:80%
would I have come to find you?

00:23:51.200 --> 00:23:52.680 line:80%
Would I have worried about you
getting hurt

00:23:52.680 --> 00:23:54.680 line:80%
and gone to the battlefield for you?

00:23:58.510 --> 00:23:59.640 line:80%
The one you like

00:24:01.090 --> 00:24:02.110 line:80%
is Yan Zheng.

00:24:03.910 --> 00:24:05.310 line:80%
I've thought it through.

00:24:05.680 --> 00:24:07.350 line:80%
No matter whether
you're Yan Zheng or Xie Zheng,

00:24:07.350 --> 00:24:08.390 line:80%
I like you.

00:24:10.110 --> 00:24:11.040 line:80%
Are you

00:24:12.480 --> 00:24:13.550 line:80%
trying to cheer me up?

00:24:13.550 --> 00:24:16.610 line:80%
I'm not trying to cheer you up.
Every word I said is true.

00:24:17.760 --> 00:24:19.240 line:80%
When you were Yan Zheng,

00:24:19.590 --> 00:24:22.590 line:80%
all we worried about every day
was daily necessities.

00:24:23.440 --> 00:24:26.100 line:80%
You'd copy books and write essays
to make money,

00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:29.230 line:80%
and I'd butcher pigs and sell meat.

00:24:29.850 --> 00:24:31.910 line:80%
Whatever difficulties we encountered,

00:24:31.910 --> 00:24:35.040 line:80%
we managed to get through them
by supporting each other.

00:24:36.200 --> 00:24:38.660 line:80%
But now, you're Marquis of Wu'an,
Xie Zheng.

00:24:40.050 --> 00:24:42.050 line:80%
There's nothing I can do to help you.

00:24:43.480 --> 00:24:44.520 line:80%
And I don't know

00:24:45.830 --> 00:24:47.180 line:80%
what you're busy with

00:24:47.390 --> 00:24:49.050 line:80%
or what you're worried about.

00:24:49.830 --> 00:24:51.440 line:80%
My mother once told me

00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:53.170 line:80%
that between husband and wife,

00:24:53.550 --> 00:24:55.070 line:80%
they must be understanding

00:24:55.070 --> 00:24:57.420 line:80%
and support each other to make it last.

00:24:59.070 --> 00:25:00.330 line:80%
Those unhappy couples

00:25:00.890 --> 00:25:02.630 line:80%
all finish their lives

00:25:02.630 --> 00:25:04.870 line:80%
without learning how to be understanding.

00:25:04.870 --> 00:25:06.200 line:80%
Their feelings and such

00:25:06.830 --> 00:25:08.290 line:80%
have long since worn away.

00:25:09.440 --> 00:25:10.440 line:80%
I don't want that.

00:25:14.960 --> 00:25:15.760 line:80%
Changyu.

00:25:16.800 --> 00:25:19.390 line:80%
Status is just an illusion.

00:25:20.480 --> 00:25:22.960 line:80%
How we feel for each other
is what matters most.

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:25.020 line:80%
Of course I know your feelings for me.

00:25:28.200 --> 00:25:29.440 line:80%
Actually, that day,

00:25:30.960 --> 00:25:33.220 line:80%
I intended to make a clean break with you.

00:25:34.340 --> 00:25:37.430 line:80%
But hearing you talk about
our time in Lin'an

00:25:37.720 --> 00:25:39.350 line:80%
and say you wanted to go back there
with me

00:25:39.350 --> 00:25:40.680 line:80%
and rebuild our home...

00:25:44.110 --> 00:25:45.870 line:80%
I'm not made of stone, you know?

00:25:47.590 --> 00:25:48.690 line:80%
I can be touched,

00:25:49.550 --> 00:25:51.410 line:80%
and I can feel reluctant to let go.

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:57.660 line:80%
Right now, there is something

00:25:58.110 --> 00:25:59.200 line:80%
I must do—

00:26:00.310 --> 00:26:01.640 line:80%
I must go save Qianqian.

00:26:05.350 --> 00:26:06.280 line:80%
But you know

00:26:07.150 --> 00:26:09.480 line:80%
those who took Yu Qianqian aren't simple.

00:26:09.720 --> 00:26:10.910 line:80%
You may not be able

00:26:11.830 --> 00:26:12.960 line:80%
to save her on your own.

00:26:12.960 --> 00:26:14.390 line:80%
I have to try to find out.

00:26:19.110 --> 00:26:19.970 line:80%
How about this?

00:26:21.150 --> 00:26:23.520 line:80%
I'll take revenge for Lin'an for you.

00:26:24.280 --> 00:26:26.350 line:80%
I'll help you find the people
who're missing,

00:26:26.350 --> 00:26:28.910 line:80%
and I'll save Yu Qianqian for you.

00:26:29.550 --> 00:26:31.550 line:80%
Don't take the risk yourself, okay?

00:26:34.760 --> 00:26:35.760 line:80%
I like you,

00:26:37.680 --> 00:26:40.140 line:80%
but I can't rely on you
for the rest of my life.

00:26:40.930 --> 00:26:43.040 line:80%
That way, I wouldn't be me.

00:26:48.200 --> 00:26:48.800 line:80%
Okay.

00:26:51.260 --> 00:26:52.190 line:80%
I know

00:26:53.040 --> 00:26:54.900 line:80%
that once you've made a decision,

00:26:55.150 --> 00:26:57.680 line:80%
you certainly won't
change your mind easily.

00:27:14.240 --> 00:27:15.100 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:27:16.940 --> 00:27:18.620 line:80%
May I come in?

00:27:21.910 --> 00:27:22.630 line:80%
Come on in.

00:27:28.720 --> 00:27:31.540 line:80%
Headmaster, what brings you here suddenly?

00:27:32.520 --> 00:27:33.380 line:80%
Your Highness,

00:27:34.180 --> 00:27:35.070 line:80%
your shoes.

00:27:41.610 --> 00:27:42.670 line:80%
You repaired them?

00:27:45.310 --> 00:27:47.870 line:80%
A patrolling soldier found them
by chance last night,

00:27:47.870 --> 00:27:49.430 line:80%
so I did a little repair.

00:27:50.150 --> 00:27:52.080 line:80%
I hope Your Highness doesn't mind.

00:27:55.910 --> 00:27:58.590 line:80%
Headmaster, please don't do
such trivial things in the future.

00:27:58.590 --> 00:27:59.850 line:80%
I won't appreciate it.

00:28:13.480 --> 00:28:14.340 line:80%
I take my leave.

00:28:25.630 --> 00:28:28.690 line:80%
Headmaster, stop using these little tricks
to fool me.

00:28:32.660 --> 00:28:34.320 line:80%
You... What's wrong with you?

00:28:40.330 --> 00:28:41.460 line:80%
It's almost dawn.

00:28:42.240 --> 00:28:43.240 line:80%
I must go,

00:28:43.870 --> 00:28:45.470 line:80%
or I won't catch up with them.

00:28:56.290 --> 00:28:57.260 line:80%
Then tell me

00:28:58.520 --> 00:28:59.390 line:80%
you like me.

00:29:05.930 --> 00:29:06.690 line:80%
Say it.

00:29:11.400 --> 00:29:12.690 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:29:12.720 --> 00:29:15.250 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:29:15.830 --> 00:29:16.880 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:29:16.900 --> 00:29:19.350 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:29:19.930 --> 00:29:23.970 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:29:24.410 --> 00:29:28.050 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:29:28.900 --> 00:29:29.790 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:29:29.810 --> 00:29:32.330 line:80%
♪ Will not be like sand
slipping into the sea ♪

00:29:33.570 --> 00:29:34.510 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:29:34.540 --> 00:29:36.980 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:29:37.410 --> 00:29:41.610 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:29:38.260 --> 00:29:41.800 line:80%
[Xie]

00:29:42.090 --> 00:29:52.770 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:29:50.000 --> 00:29:52.590 line:80%
Find an elite squad and have them
protect Fan Changyu in secret.

00:29:52.590 --> 00:29:53.160 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:56.390 --> 00:29:58.520 line:80%
Headmaster, you're so badly injured.

00:29:58.760 --> 00:30:00.490 line:80%
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:30:01.050 --> 00:30:02.980 line:80%
When I thought you were lying to me,

00:30:03.680 --> 00:30:05.480 line:80%
why didn't you tell me the truth?

00:30:06.310 --> 00:30:07.000 line:80%
Before,

00:30:09.310 --> 00:30:10.590 line:80%
I did indeed lie to you.

00:30:11.750 --> 00:30:12.820 line:80%
So today,

00:30:14.290 --> 00:30:16.610 line:80%
I've got no right to defend myself.

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:24.040 line:80%
I'll

00:30:25.550 --> 00:30:27.760 line:80%
just find another herb for treatment.

00:30:28.280 --> 00:30:30.210 line:80%
Please rest early, Your Highness.

00:30:31.110 --> 00:30:32.520 line:80%
Whether you're fine or not

00:30:32.520 --> 00:30:34.320 line:80%
is up to me, the royal physician.

00:30:34.640 --> 00:30:35.520 line:80%
Turn around.

00:30:36.280 --> 00:30:37.130 line:80%
Turn around!

00:30:44.800 --> 00:30:47.360 line:80%
Headmaster, you carry such authority
in the academy,

00:30:47.360 --> 00:30:49.350 line:80%
and you're so brave and wise
on the battlefield.

00:30:49.350 --> 00:30:52.080 line:80%
Why are you so careless
when it comes to yourself?

00:30:58.110 --> 00:30:58.870 line:80%
What are you laughing at, Headmaster?

00:30:58.870 --> 00:31:00.130 line:80%
You're still injured.

00:31:00.150 --> 00:31:01.880 line:80%
Don't, don't... I'm ticklish.

00:31:02.150 --> 00:31:04.480 line:80%
You're dying! Why are you still laughing?

00:31:05.910 --> 00:31:06.440 line:80%
I...

00:31:09.340 --> 00:31:11.970 line:80%
What I want to say is, my feelings for you

00:31:13.390 --> 00:31:15.050 line:80%
are actually like my illness—

00:31:16.390 --> 00:31:18.590 line:80%
though it may seem like I've deceived you,

00:31:18.590 --> 00:31:21.120 line:80%
it was never my intention.

00:31:22.830 --> 00:31:23.890 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:31:28.550 --> 00:31:29.590 line:80%
I'll speak plainly.

00:31:29.590 --> 00:31:30.520 line:80%
-I…
-Counselor!

00:31:33.440 --> 00:31:35.370 line:80%
His Lordship has returned to camp.

00:31:37.230 --> 00:31:38.200 line:80%
Even if the sky falls,

00:31:38.200 --> 00:31:39.690 line:80%
I must finish saying this.

00:31:40.200 --> 00:31:41.800 line:80%
Finish it when you come back.

00:31:42.390 --> 00:31:44.050 line:80%
I'll wait for you to come back.

00:31:52.480 --> 00:31:55.260 line:80%
General Shiyi, please tell His Lordship

00:31:55.440 --> 00:31:56.830 line:80%
that Counselor has internal injuries

00:31:56.830 --> 00:31:58.230 line:80%
and shouldn't overwork.

00:32:00.200 --> 00:32:02.630 line:80%
If Counselor's condition worsens
when he returns,

00:32:02.630 --> 00:32:04.200 line:80%
I'll hold His Lordship accountable.

00:32:04.200 --> 00:32:04.800 line:80%
Yes.

00:32:06.150 --> 00:32:06.720 line:80%
Then...

00:32:07.440 --> 00:32:08.240 line:80%
I'll go now.

00:32:22.000 --> 00:32:23.260 line:80%
Did you bring her back?

00:32:23.440 --> 00:32:24.070 line:80%
She left.

00:32:24.630 --> 00:32:26.030 line:80%
She has her own thoughts,

00:32:26.040 --> 00:32:27.440 line:80%
and I respect her wishes.

00:32:29.070 --> 00:32:30.390 line:80%
This Mrs. Fan is actually able

00:32:30.390 --> 00:32:32.870 line:80%
to make the Marquis of Wu'an
so melancholy—

00:32:33.570 --> 00:32:35.230 line:80%
she must be quite a character.

00:32:37.800 --> 00:32:40.130 line:80%
Her Highness is returning to the Capital.

00:32:40.150 --> 00:32:42.550 line:80%
I'll leave her protection to you.

00:32:42.720 --> 00:32:45.000 line:80%
Her Highness has promised Mrs. Fan

00:32:45.000 --> 00:32:46.760 line:80%
to send Changning back to Lin'an.

00:32:46.760 --> 00:32:49.310 line:80%
After that, whether she chooses to
stay in the Capital

00:32:49.310 --> 00:32:50.680 line:80%
or remain in the military camp,

00:32:50.680 --> 00:32:52.340 line:80%
I'll also respect her wishes.

00:32:53.800 --> 00:32:55.600 line:80%
That's not what you said before.

00:32:55.800 --> 00:32:58.280 line:80%
Back when Li Huai'an was investigating me
in Lin'an,

00:32:58.280 --> 00:33:01.280 line:80%
he soon returned to the Capital
to court Her Highness.

00:33:01.390 --> 00:33:03.120 line:80%
That was your doing, wasn't it?

00:33:05.830 --> 00:33:06.550 line:80%
Sort of.

00:33:08.410 --> 00:33:09.470 line:80%
But not entirely.

00:33:12.070 --> 00:33:13.930 line:80%
When emotions surge in the heart,

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:15.400 line:80%
how can one control them?

00:33:16.800 --> 00:33:19.000 line:80%
Better to stop them before they sprout,

00:33:19.200 --> 00:33:21.400 line:80%
to avoid falling into the swamp of love.

00:33:23.070 --> 00:33:24.800 line:80%
Informing Consort Dowager An

00:33:24.800 --> 00:33:26.240 line:80%
about Her Highness being at the academy

00:33:26.240 --> 00:33:27.680 line:80%
was indeed my doing.

00:33:28.240 --> 00:33:31.640 line:80%
As for Her Highness courting Li Huai'an...

00:33:32.270 --> 00:33:34.070 line:80%
It was indeed unexpected.

00:33:35.280 --> 00:33:37.610 line:80%
Given Consort Dowager An's temperament,

00:33:37.870 --> 00:33:39.470 line:80%
she definitely won't agree.

00:33:41.110 --> 00:33:42.590 line:80%
This is the last time Her Highness

00:33:42.590 --> 00:33:45.650 line:80%
personally makes medicinal food
for you, Mr. Gongsun.

00:33:46.870 --> 00:33:47.870 line:80%
You go ahead first.

00:33:47.870 --> 00:33:50.200 line:80%
My horse is fast.
I'll catch up right away.

00:33:54.830 --> 00:33:55.760 line:80%
Let's get going.

00:34:00.200 --> 00:34:01.460 line:80%
All troops, listen up!

00:34:01.570 --> 00:34:02.890 line:80%
To Lucheng!

00:34:03.280 --> 00:34:04.240 line:80%
Yes!

00:34:17.510 --> 00:34:23.030 line:80%
[Villa in the west suburb of Lucheng]

00:34:33.490 --> 00:34:36.060 line:80%
[Lord Changxin, Sui Tuo]

00:34:37.600 --> 00:34:38.240 line:80%
Father.

00:34:52.870 --> 00:34:54.950 line:80%
I never should have believed
your nonsense.

00:34:54.950 --> 00:34:57.030 line:80%
So much for your infallible strategy.

00:34:57.030 --> 00:34:59.160 line:80%
We are suffering defeat after defeat.

00:34:59.200 --> 00:35:01.310 line:80%
Not only did we lose General Shi Hu,

00:35:02.280 --> 00:35:04.640 line:80%
but Yuanqing almost lost his life too!

00:35:10.680 --> 00:35:11.470 line:80%
What?

00:35:12.280 --> 00:35:13.160 line:80%
Unconvinced?

00:35:13.560 --> 00:35:14.960 line:80%
Did I wrongly accuse you?

00:35:22.280 --> 00:35:23.680 line:80%
When you were young,

00:35:24.470 --> 00:35:26.090 line:80%
you used to be cheerful.

00:35:26.120 --> 00:35:27.600 line:80%
But a fire turned you into

00:35:27.600 --> 00:35:28.680 line:80%
what you are now!

00:35:33.120 --> 00:35:35.050 line:80%
Let me make this clear to you today:

00:35:35.800 --> 00:35:38.120 line:80%
even if something happens to Yuanqing,

00:35:38.990 --> 00:35:39.800 line:80%
the throne

00:35:40.390 --> 00:35:41.720 line:80%
will still not be yours!

00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:46.040 line:80%
I have never coveted the throne,

00:35:46.640 --> 00:35:48.770 line:80%
nor do I wish to compete with Yuanqing.

00:35:49.130 --> 00:35:50.690 line:80%
If I'm lying,

00:35:51.160 --> 00:35:52.120 line:80%
may heaven strike me down.

00:35:52.120 --> 00:35:53.000 line:80%
Yuanhuai.

00:35:54.080 --> 00:35:56.880 line:80%
Between us brothers,
is an oath really necessary?

00:35:57.060 --> 00:35:58.720 line:80%
Why curse yourself like that?

00:35:59.080 --> 00:35:59.680 line:80%
Here.

00:36:00.430 --> 00:36:01.310 line:80%
Yuanqing.

00:36:01.720 --> 00:36:02.970 line:80%
We are at war.

00:36:03.390 --> 00:36:04.390 line:80%
Mind your status.

00:36:04.560 --> 00:36:06.430 line:80%
Father, the enemy's at our doorstep.

00:36:06.430 --> 00:36:07.680 line:80%
Please stop putting on airs.

00:36:07.680 --> 00:36:09.340 line:80%
It's just the three of us here.

00:36:10.120 --> 00:36:11.240 line:80%
If outsiders knew

00:36:11.240 --> 00:36:12.800 line:80%
that we were fighting amongst ourselves,

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:15.350 line:80%
they would surely take advantage of
the chaos.

00:36:15.350 --> 00:36:17.810 line:80%
Even the wise are not always free
from error.

00:36:18.680 --> 00:36:21.410 line:80%
Yuanhuai already did his best
against Xie Zheng.

00:36:22.350 --> 00:36:24.810 line:80%
If Yuanhuai hadn't sent Shi Yue
to save me,

00:36:25.180 --> 00:36:27.030 line:80%
Xie Zheng would have tied me up
on the battlefield

00:36:27.030 --> 00:36:27.960 line:80%
to threaten you.

00:36:30.860 --> 00:36:32.660 line:80%
Children are nothing but debts.

00:36:38.280 --> 00:36:39.030 line:80%
Yuanhuai.

00:36:41.280 --> 00:36:43.200 line:80%
Go and reorganize the logistics.

00:36:44.080 --> 00:36:45.140 line:80%
The Chongzhou Army

00:36:47.600 --> 00:36:49.310 line:80%
cannot afford a third defeat.

00:36:50.990 --> 00:36:52.320 line:80%
As you command, Father.

00:37:05.600 --> 00:37:09.360 line:80%
Ever since he was burned
in that fire 17 years ago,

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:12.940 line:80%
he has become as stubborn as a mule,

00:37:13.240 --> 00:37:14.680 line:80%
perverse and paranoid,

00:37:15.470 --> 00:37:17.830 line:80%
as if possessed by a demon.

00:37:17.850 --> 00:37:19.980 line:80%
Father, please don't blame Yuanhuai.

00:37:20.240 --> 00:37:22.440 line:80%
Anyone who suffered such a great ordeal

00:37:22.720 --> 00:37:25.050 line:80%
would inevitably change in temperament.

00:37:25.390 --> 00:37:27.080 line:80%
Yuanhuai has always been kind to us.

00:37:27.080 --> 00:37:29.410 line:80%
He harbors absolutely no ill intentions.

00:37:30.430 --> 00:37:32.490 line:80%
I hope you will see the truth, Father.

00:37:42.600 --> 00:37:43.640 line:80%
Sui Tuo.

00:37:45.200 --> 00:37:47.210 line:80%
I indeed do not want your throne.

00:37:48.310 --> 00:37:49.350 line:80%
What I want

00:37:52.390 --> 00:37:54.250 line:80%
is the lives of you father and son.

00:38:14.310 --> 00:38:14.910 line:80%
Charge!

00:38:30.010 --> 00:38:30.690 line:80%
Bao'er.

00:38:31.670 --> 00:38:32.670 line:80%
Quick, run!

00:38:32.990 --> 00:38:33.880 line:80%
Go!

00:38:42.680 --> 00:38:43.910 line:80%
Take this.

00:38:44.280 --> 00:38:47.120 line:80%
Blow it whenever you are in danger,

00:38:47.120 --> 00:38:49.180 line:80%
and someone will come to protect you.

00:39:02.720 --> 00:39:03.470 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:39:30.340 --> 00:39:30.940 line:80%
Retreat!

00:39:35.530 --> 00:39:36.720 line:80%
We're from Jizhou.

00:39:36.740 --> 00:39:39.140 line:80%
We're not... We're not the Chongzhou Army.

00:39:47.350 --> 00:39:48.080 line:80%
Bao'er?

00:39:54.030 --> 00:39:55.750 line:80%
Uncle Yan!

00:39:56.760 --> 00:39:57.760 line:80%
Are you all right?

00:40:03.030 --> 00:40:06.130 line:80%
Uncle Yan, I'm so scared.

00:40:06.510 --> 00:40:09.070 line:80%
Bad guys took my mother away.

00:40:09.100 --> 00:40:09.930 line:80%
It's okay.

00:40:10.280 --> 00:40:11.680 line:80%
Everything will be okay.

00:40:17.750 --> 00:40:18.300 line:80%
[Sui]

00:40:18.300 --> 00:40:21.700 line:80%
[Villa in the west suburb of Lucheng]

00:40:39.620 --> 00:40:40.410 line:80%
Miss me?

00:40:49.270 --> 00:40:50.360 line:80%
Why are you staring?

00:40:50.360 --> 00:40:51.090 line:80%
Come sit.

00:41:03.080 --> 00:41:04.080 line:80%
I personally made

00:41:04.500 --> 00:41:07.810 line:80%
my specialty,
snowy-clear soup with steamed bread.

00:41:12.310 --> 00:41:13.080 line:80%
Have a taste.

00:41:19.680 --> 00:41:20.640 line:80%
This soup...

00:41:21.260 --> 00:41:22.990 line:80%
You didn't poison it, did you?

00:41:27.190 --> 00:41:28.110 line:80%
Are you scared?

00:41:54.200 --> 00:41:55.640 line:80%
Even if it were poisoned,

00:41:56.490 --> 00:41:58.100 line:80%
as long as it's from you,

00:41:58.950 --> 00:42:00.200 line:80%
I would drink it.

00:42:02.240 --> 00:42:03.080 line:80%
Very well.

00:42:04.110 --> 00:42:06.170 line:80%
Then I'll really poison it next time.

00:42:14.320 --> 00:42:17.240 line:80%
I would drink it gladly.

00:42:35.090 --> 00:42:36.700 line:80%
Just for a moment,

00:42:37.490 --> 00:42:39.620 line:80%
I felt that spending the rest of my life

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:41.530 line:80%
like this would actually be

00:42:43.680 --> 00:42:44.800 line:80%
quite nice.

00:42:58.640 --> 00:43:00.390 line:80%
If our army hadn't taken a detour,

00:43:00.390 --> 00:43:02.050 line:80%
we wouldn't have run into you.

00:43:07.300 --> 00:43:10.260 line:80%
Heaven truly blesses the worthy.

00:43:13.720 --> 00:43:14.510 line:80%
Untie him.

00:43:22.210 --> 00:43:23.250 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.

00:43:23.680 --> 00:43:25.600 line:80%
You were hard to find.

00:43:26.150 --> 00:43:27.780 line:80%
I owe Your Lordship my life.

00:43:28.720 --> 00:43:30.920 line:80%
If you ever need me, Your Lordship,

00:43:31.080 --> 00:43:32.990 line:80%
I'll do anything for you.

00:43:34.080 --> 00:43:36.480 line:80%
When you came to find me
in Lin'an last year,

00:43:36.560 --> 00:43:37.890 line:80%
you said the same thing.

00:43:38.640 --> 00:43:40.430 line:80%
Please calm down, Your Lordship.

00:43:40.430 --> 00:43:42.310 line:80%
I had no choice.

00:43:43.120 --> 00:43:44.650 line:80%
The 200,000 piculs of grain

00:43:44.870 --> 00:43:46.120 line:80%
was indeed a trap.

00:43:46.720 --> 00:43:48.560 line:80%
But luckily, Your Lordship foiled it,

00:43:48.560 --> 00:43:50.680 line:80%
so the villains didn't succeed.

00:43:51.430 --> 00:43:52.950 line:80%
You told me back then

00:43:53.120 --> 00:43:54.990 line:80%
that you were from the Eastern Palace.

00:43:54.990 --> 00:43:56.430 line:80%
Was that true or false?

00:43:58.310 --> 00:44:00.280 line:80%
My mother, Lan,

00:44:01.120 --> 00:44:04.120 line:80%
was once Crown Princess Chengde's
most trusted maid.

00:44:04.390 --> 00:44:07.240 line:80%
Later, upon reaching a certain age,
she was fortunate enough to leave the palace.

00:44:07.240 --> 00:44:09.370 line:80%
On the surface, she married my father;

00:44:09.560 --> 00:44:12.160 line:80%
but in secret, she helped
Crown Princess Chengde

00:44:12.160 --> 00:44:14.290 line:80%
manage her assets outside the palace.

00:44:15.080 --> 00:44:15.910 line:80%
Master,

00:44:16.170 --> 00:44:18.460 line:80%
I noticed it's a bit dark in here.

00:44:18.760 --> 00:44:20.760 line:80%
Shall I light two more lamps for you?

00:44:23.040 --> 00:44:24.680 line:80%
The fire in the Eastern Palace

00:44:24.680 --> 00:44:26.600 line:80%
was set by the Crown Princess herself,

00:44:26.600 --> 00:44:29.990 line:80%
to give Imperial Eldest Grandson
a chance at survival.

00:44:33.690 --> 00:44:35.220 line:80%
Then who was behind the plot

00:44:35.350 --> 00:44:36.950 line:80%
against the Eastern Palace?

00:44:38.160 --> 00:44:39.350 line:80%
I have no idea.

00:44:39.990 --> 00:44:41.640 line:80%
My mother only received
the Crown Princess's letter

00:44:41.640 --> 00:44:43.620 line:80%
after the fire.

00:44:43.990 --> 00:44:47.320 line:80%
But the letter didn't mention anything
about the murderer.

00:44:47.680 --> 00:44:48.720 line:80%
Please spare me, Eldest Young Master!

00:44:48.720 --> 00:44:51.750 line:80%
I truly didn't know you were here,
Eldest Young Master.

00:44:51.750 --> 00:44:54.200 line:80%
Is the Imperial Eldest Grandson
still alive?

00:44:54.200 --> 00:44:54.870 line:80%
Yes.

00:44:56.200 --> 00:44:57.390 line:80%
He's now

00:44:58.030 --> 00:44:59.630 line:80%
Lord Changxin's eldest son.

00:45:00.600 --> 00:45:02.160 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai?

00:45:06.430 --> 00:45:08.900 line:80%
[Post-Credits Scene]

00:45:24.350 --> 00:45:25.750 line:80%
You've got more than just

00:45:27.160 --> 00:45:29.090 line:80%
cuts and sword wounds on your body.

00:45:34.360 --> 00:45:35.190 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:45:37.890 --> 00:45:39.100 line:80%
It must hurt a lot.

00:45:41.690 --> 00:45:42.430 line:80%
It's okay.

00:45:44.090 --> 00:45:45.820 line:80%
You're just a young lady.

00:45:46.640 --> 00:45:47.950 line:80%
With wounds like this,

00:45:48.730 --> 00:45:49.930 line:80%
how could it not hurt?

00:45:58.430 --> 00:46:00.680 line:80%
You... You're hurt here too.

00:46:00.880 --> 00:46:01.930 line:80%
It's all red.

00:46:03.430 --> 00:46:05.890 line:80%
I probably bumped it
on the battlefield too.

00:46:09.560 --> 00:46:10.760 line:80%
Doesn't seem like it.

00:46:11.760 --> 00:46:14.350 line:80%
All your other bruises are dark,

00:46:14.990 --> 00:46:16.550 line:80%
but this one

00:46:16.640 --> 00:46:18.510 line:80%
looks quite fresh.

00:46:19.510 --> 00:46:20.490 line:80%
It's weird.

00:46:21.080 --> 00:46:24.340 line:80%
I've never read about
anything like this in medical books.

00:46:24.640 --> 00:46:26.800 line:80%
Fresh...

00:46:40.550 --> 00:46:42.840 line:80%
I must have gotten it

00:46:43.080 --> 00:46:44.390 line:80%
when I fell and hit a stone.